  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BodyRecords</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offers a distinctive fusion of bodycam perspective, eerie liminal spaces, and immersive microphone sensitivity - be cautious, your voice can give you away. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set within expansive, atmospheric environments, players must explore, solve puzzles, and evade dangers while gathering vital information to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In BodyRecords, teamwork is crucial. Players must collaborate closely to solve puzzles and progress. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bodycam Perspective</strong>: Experience immersive gameplay through a bodycam view that’s central to the action. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Microphone Sensitivity</strong>: Your voice and sound affect the game, adding tension and immersion. Be careful - the creepy creatures around you react to any noise. <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/6b589cd2c4f3f8e75afafe54955efe06.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/6b589cd2c4f3f8e75afafe54955efe06.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/6b589cd2c4f3f8e75afafe54955efe06.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle-Solving</strong>: Dive into intuitive yet engaging puzzles that enrich the exploration. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>True Cooperative Play</strong>: Meaningful teamwork is required to progress, making collaboration essential for survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death is not the end</strong> - when you die, you enter the Backrooms, a mysterious dimension with a chance to escape and return to the real world. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, solve, escape - work together to uncover the local mysteries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So are you ready to capture your journey?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BodyRecords</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offers a distinctive fusion of bodycam perspective, eerie liminal spaces, and immersive microphone sensitivity - be cautious, your voice can give you away. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set within expansive, atmospheric environments, players must explore, solve puzzles, and evade dangers while gathering vital information to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In BodyRecords, teamwork is crucial. Players must collaborate closely to solve puzzles and progress. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bodycam Perspective</strong>: Experience immersive gameplay through a bodycam view that’s central to the action. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Microphone Sensitivity</strong>: Your voice and sound affect the game, adding tension and immersion. Be careful - the creepy creatures around you react to any noise. <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/6b589cd2c4f3f8e75afafe54955efe06.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/6b589cd2c4f3f8e75afafe54955efe06.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/6b589cd2c4f3f8e75afafe54955efe06.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle-Solving</strong>: Dive into intuitive yet engaging puzzles that enrich the exploration. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>True Cooperative Play</strong>: Meaningful teamwork is required to progress, making collaboration essential for survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death is not the end</strong> - when you die, you enter the Backrooms, a mysterious dimension with a chance to escape and return to the real world. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, solve, escape - work together to uncover the local mysteries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So are you ready to capture your journey?</p>",
